---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
const imageSrc = '/path-to-your-image.jpg';
const linkHref = '/your-link';
const {text} = Astro.props;
import Buttum from "../components/Buttum.astro";
export const submitEndpoint = "/api/submit-tattoo-request"; // Replace with your backend endpoint
---

<MainLayout metatitle="PANACHE">
    <!-- Overskrift, linje og tekst -->
    <div class="H1tattoo">
        <h1>TATTOO ARTISTS</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="line"></div>

    <p class="ptattoo">
        Step into Panache’s tattoo studio, where creativity meets individuality, and every design tells a story—yours!
        With
        three talented, resident tattoo artists, this is not your average tattoo joint. Our small but mighty team keeps
        it
        personal, keeping the vibe chill, inspiring, and brimming with creativity.<br><br>

        Whether you're after something bold, intricate, or downright quirky, our artists are here to bring your vision
        to life.
        Each tattoo session is by appointment only because we believe in giving every masterpiece the time and attention
        it
        deserves. <br><br>Slide into our DMs on Instagram to book your spot and let’s create something unforgettable!

        At Panache, tattoos aren’t just ink—they’re art, memories, and a reflection of you. Plus, with wine and art just
        steps
        away, why not make it an all-day creative adventure?
    </p>

    <!-- Tattooo Artist / grdi_container -->
    <div class="grid-container">
        <div>
            <img src="/bilder/jacob.webp" alt="Descriptive Alt Text" class="image" />
        </div>
        <div class="text-content">
            <h2 class="navn">Jacob Max Moltke</h2>
            <p>Jacob isn’t just a tattoo artist; they’re a storyteller with a needle. Known for bold lines and striking
                designs, Jacob
                specializes in blackwork and abstract pieces that turn skin into wearable art.<br><br> If you want a tattoo that
                stands out and
                sparks conversation, Jacob is your go-to.<br><br> Whether it’s a minimalist statement or a full-sleeve
                masterpiece, they’ll make
                sure your ink speaks volumes.</p>

              <a class="Buttum" href="https://www.instagram.com/maxmoltke/">
<Buttum  text="@maxmoltke"> </Buttum>
</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-container middle-grid">
        <div class="text-content">
            <h2 class="navn">Alistair</h2>
            <p>Alistair is all about bringing color and fun to your tattoo dreams.<br><br> From vibrant watercolor effects to
                playful, illustrative
                designs, Alistair´s swork is perfect for those who want their personality to shine through their ink.<br><br>
                With a love for bold
                hues and creative storytelling, Alistair´ tattoos are as lively and unique as the clients who wear them.
            </p>
               <a class="Buttum" href="https://www.instagram.com/alistairtattoos/">
<Buttum  text=" @alistairtattoos"> </Buttum>
</a>
           
        </div>
        <div>
            <img src="/bilder/alistair.webp" alt="Descriptive Alt Text" class="image" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-container">
        <div>
            <img src="/bilder/anna.webp" alt="Descriptive Alt Text" class="image" />
        </div>
        <div class="text-content">
            <h2  class="navn">Anna Tietze Borregaard</h2>
            <p>Anna is the queen of precision and detail. Her expertise lies in delicate fine-line tattoos, floral
                motifs, and intricate
                patterns.<br><br> Looking for something elegant, soft, and timeless? Anna´s got you covered. <br><br>Her steady hand and
                artistic eye
                bring even the smallest details to life, ensuring your tattoo feels personal and unique.</p>
                  <a class="Buttum" href="https://www.instagram.com/tatietzetoo/">
<Buttum  text="@tatietzetoo"> </Buttum>
</a>
           
        </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FORM -->
    <form action={submitEndpoint} method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <div class="h2tattoo">
            <h2>GET A TATTOO</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="p2tattoo">
            <p>Ready to bring your tattoo idea to life? Fill out the form to request an appointment with one of our talented artists. Share your vision, describe your tattoo idea, and upload any inspiration photos. Once submitted, we’ll get back to you to confirm details and discuss the next steps. Let’s create something unforgettable together!






</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Full Name -->
        <label for="full-name">Full Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="full-name" name="full_name" placeholder="Enter your full name" required />

        <!-- Phone Number -->
        <label for="phone-number">Phone Number</label>
        <input type="tel" id="phone-number" name="phone_number" placeholder="Enter your phone number" required />

        <!-- Email Address -->
        <label for="email-address">Email Address</label>
        <input type="email" id="email-address" name="email_address" placeholder="Enter your email address" required />

        <!-- Tattoo Artist -->
        <label for="tattoo-artist">Tattoo Artist</label>
        <select id="tattoo-artist" name="tattoo_artist" required>
            <option value="">Select your tattoo artist</option>
            <option value="artist1">JACOB</option>
            <option value="artist2">ALISTAIR</option>
            <option value="artist3">ANNA</option>
            <option value="artist3">Random</option>
        </select>

        <!-- Tattoo Description -->
        <label for="tattoo-description">Please Describe Your Tattoo</label>
        <textarea id="tattoo-description" name="tattoo_description" rows="5" placeholder="Describe your tattoo idea"
            required></textarea>


        <!-- Upload Photo -->
        <label for="photo-upload">Upload Photo Inspiration</label>
        <input type="file" id="photo-upload" name="photo_upload" accept="image/*" />

        <!-- Submit Button -->
 <Buttum  text="Submit Request"> </Buttum>
    </form>


</MainLayout>


    <style>
        @media (max-width: 800px) {

            .grid-container {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 2rem;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 10px;
                margin: 30px;
            }

            .text-content {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.5rem;
                align-items: flex-start;
                justify-content: flex-start;
               
            }

            .middle-grid {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                /* Stack the items vertically */
            }

            .middle-grid .text-content {
                order: 2;
                /* Move text after image */
            }

            .middle-grid .image {
                order: 1;
                /* Make sure the image appears first */
            }


            .image {
                width: 100%;
                /* Ensure image takes up full width on mobile */
            }
        }

        .H1tattoo {
            text-align: center;
           
        }

        .line {
            width: 70%;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: black;
            margin: 20px auto;
          
        }

        @media (min-width: 800px) {
            .grid-container {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 1rem;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 40px;
            }
        }

        .ptattoo {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .image {
            width: 80%;
            height: auto;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .text-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
           
         
        }
        .navn{
            color: #ab0000;
        }

        .link {
            color: #ab0000;
            ;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }


        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin-top: 100px;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            /* Rounded corners for a soft look */
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Light shadow for depth */
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .h2tattoo {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: xx-large;
            color: #ab0000;
            font-optical-sizing: auto;
            font-weight: weight;
            font-style: normal;
            font-variation-settings: "wdth" 100;

        }

        .p2tattoo {
            
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: "Noto Sans Mono", serif;
            font-optical-sizing: auto;
            font-weight: weight;
            font-style: normal;
            font-variation-settings: "wdth" 100;
        }

        label {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: "Noto Sans Mono", serif;
  font-optical-sizing: auto;
  font-weight: weight;
  font-style: normal;
  font-variation-settings: "wdth" 100;
        }

   
.Buttum{
 display: flex;
  margin: 0 auto;
  align-items: flex-end; /* Pushes content to the bottom */
  height: 100%;
}

    </style>